  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nChange password from Profile view. After new password is entered and confirm button is clicked, after some time operation silently fails with the error in the log:\r\n```\r\nerror:   topics=\"privacy-service\" tid=62524 file=service.nim:99 procName=changePassword errDesription=\"rename /tmp/1429909632-v4.db /home/user/work/projects/Status/status-desktop/Status/data/0x8e5b0d6c8c8bbb112889c5932549cad6ce15dfbf09c493ceb933fe0b5b176da9-v4.db: invalid cross-device link\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nSettings->Profile->Change password-> Enter new password -> Change password and restart status\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nPassword changed successfully\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nSilent error in the log\r\n### Additional Information\r\nI have `/tmp` and `/home` directories on different partitions.\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.13.1-rc.1; another setup is commits status-desktop 2e1b60ab067f3b77a4da2ae03cf607c69c7c488f with status-go d5203c5e539846fb090bf3583ee536ec88f8b7a4\r\n- Operating System: Ubuntu 20.04.6\r\n\r\n",
